The paper is about a new face dataset for training deep networks, which is a topic related to computer vision (cs.CV). The use of deep neural networks is also a key aspect of the paper, which suggests that it could also be relevant to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The dataset includes annotations for keypoint detection, which is a common task in multimedia (cs.MM) and image retrieval (cs.IR) research.
